Schaeuble to Examine Greece Debt Report ‘Closely,’ FAS Reports

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-05-14T15:04:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-14/schaeuble-to-examine-greece-debt-report-closely-fas-reports.html
German Finance Minister  Wolfgang Schaeuble  said he will examine the report being prepared for
June on  Greece ’s debt-tackling progress “especially closely,”
the Frankfurter Allgemeine Sonntagszeitung  reported .  Schaeuble told the newspaper that private creditors should
participate in future euro area bailouts within the framework of
the European Stability Mechanism, according to an e-mailed
version of the story to be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  